{"id":4155,"date":"2019-01-30T14:48:17","date_gmt":"2019-01-30T14:48:17","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=4155"},"modified":"2021-02-27T03:46:37","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T03:46:37","slug":"nhung-sai-lam-can-tranh-trong-thiet-ke-noi-hien-dai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/nhung-sai-lam-can-tranh-trong-thiet-ke-noi-hien-dai\/","title":{"rendered":"Nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-5574 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/44742b76955687.5c7904aa12c98.jpg\" alt=\"sai-lam-can-tranh-khi-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai\" width=\"1400\" height=\"896\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/44742b76955687.5c7904aa12c98.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/44742b76955687.5c7904aa12c98-300x192.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/44742b76955687.5c7904aa12c98-768x492.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/44742b76955687.5c7904aa12c98-1024x655.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Trong kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e9p ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n qu\u00e1 l\u1ed1 s\u1ebd l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u00f4n vinh. C\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft trang tr\u00ed ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf, \u01b0u ti\u00ean kh\u01a1i g\u1ee3i x\u00fac c\u1ea3m qua hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng th\u1ecb gi\u00e1c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 l\u01b0u \u00fd nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i bao g\u1ed3m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c nhau, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat s\u01a1 su\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea1m ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0. V\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea1n n\u00ean tham kh\u1ea3o nh\u1eefng <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\">sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1<\/a>i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia s\u1ebb d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p cho kh\u00f4ng gian nh\u1ecf <\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-5577 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/b5493876955687.5c7904aa14ae8.jpg\" alt=\"sai-lam-can-tranh-khi-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai\" width=\"1400\" height=\"941\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/b5493876955687.5c7904aa14ae8.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/b5493876955687.5c7904aa14ae8-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/b5493876955687.5c7904aa14ae8-768x516.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/b5493876955687.5c7904aa14ae8-1024x688.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, b\u1edfi vi\u1ec7c tham kh\u1ea3o qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u1eb9p, c\u00e1i g\u00ec hay c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1ed3i nh\u00e9t v\u00e0o ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft c\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p v\u00e0 t\u00f9 t\u00fang h\u01a1n. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian nh\u1ecf b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng cho kh\u00f4ng gian. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. Ph\u00e2n chia kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u00f4ng khoa h\u1ecdc &nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-5571 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/6f459276846857.5c75faf1244ba.jpg\" alt=\"sai-lam-can-tranh-khi-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai\" width=\"1400\" height=\"842\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/6f459276846857.5c75faf1244ba.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/6f459276846857.5c75faf1244ba-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/6f459276846857.5c75faf1244ba-768x462.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/6f459276846857.5c75faf1244ba-1024x616.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u00e2n chia kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch khoa h\u1ecdc l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n v\u1ebd thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. V\u00ec v\u1eady khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd ph\u00e2n chia kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t sao cho th\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 khoa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n nghi cho kh\u00f4ng gian chung v\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh. L\u01b0u \u00fd khi ph\u00e2n chia c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian trong nh\u00e0 v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh di chuy\u1ec3n gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi c\u00f3 kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u00e0.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5576\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/a8ace376955687.5c7904aa13452.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"896\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/a8ace376955687.5c7904aa13452.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/a8ace376955687.5c7904aa13452-300x192.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/a8ace376955687.5c7904aa13452-768x492.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/a8ace376955687.5c7904aa13452-1024x655.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/> <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean l\u1ed9n x\u1ed9n v\u00e0 ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p h\u01a1n. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gam m\u00e0u \u0111\u1eadm<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5573\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/12a11176846857.5c75faf123e43.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"739\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/12a11176846857.5c75faf123e43.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/12a11176846857.5c75faf123e43-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/12a11176846857.5c75faf123e43-768x405.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/12a11176846857.5c75faf123e43-1024x541.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng n\u1eefa b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i cho nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u \u0111\u1eadm, v\u00ec n\u00f3 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p v\u00e0 t\u00f9 t\u00fang h\u01a1n. M\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh, nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n cho kh\u00f4ng gian.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e9p ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n qu\u00e1 l\u1ed1 s\u1ebd l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u00f4n vinh. C\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft trang tr\u00ed ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf, \u01b0u ti\u00ean kh\u01a1i g\u1ee3i x\u00fac c\u1ea3m qua hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5571,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[154],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4155","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-chia-se-kien-thuc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4155","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4155"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4155\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5571"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4155"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\